---
title: coset_evals_to_cell (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_iter : cell = []
    q_iter --> q_append : i < FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_CELL
    q_iter --> q_return : i >= FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_CELL
    q_append --> q_iter : cell += bls_field_to_bytes(coset_evals[i])
    q_return --> [*] : return Cell(cell)

    note right of q_iter
        INV: Output Cell has exactly FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_CELL * BYTES_PER_FIELD_ELEMENT bytes
        INV: Inverse of cell_to_coset_evals for valid field elements
    end note
